  "text": "In this section, we take a brief glance retrospectively at algorithms before the deep learning era. More detailed and comprehensive coverage of these works can be found in [CITATION_1] , [CITATION_2] , [CITATION_3] , [CITATION_4] . For text detection and recognition, the attention has been the design of features.",
